                    </div></a> <span class="tm-user-info__user"><a href="/ru/users/peaceful-coder/" class="tm-user-info__username"> peaceful-coder </a> </span></span> <span class="tm-article-snippet__datetime-published"><time datetime="2022-02-27T21:14:39.000Z" title="2022-02-28, 00:14">28 февраля в 00:14</time></span>
